# 🔥 Why This Outclasses Down with the Ship

Down with the Ship = adjacency optimization.

ChronoForge = **adjacency + physics + timeline manipulation.**

Three axes instead of one.

| Layer         | Down with the Ship | ChronoForge                                 |
| ------------- | ------------------ | ------------------------------------------- |
| Spatial       | Grid adjacency     | Grid + center-of-mass + torque              |
| Synergy       | Item combos        | Item + physics + timeline loops             |
| Combat        | Deterministic auto | Probabilistic timeline branching            |
| Failure State | HP loss            | HP + structural collapse + paradox overload |

This multiplies build expression dramatically.

