* Square grid chassis
* Modules have:

  * Weight
  * Power draw
  * Heat generation
  * Structural load
  * Time cost

If you stack cannons on one side?

→ Torque imbalance
→ Recoil pushes mech backward
→ Accuracy drops

Physics becomes a build consideration.

