## 3️⃣ Time Manipulation Layer (The Killer Feature)

![Image](https://realtimevfx.com/uploads/default/original/3X/8/d/8dac61fa532db6c9bb9f6f44bc6d0a6cd44ccfd3.gif)

![Image](https://randompowergenerator.com/_astro/time-rewind.Ox9VOuF8_1jLagd.webp)

![Image](https://www.sinasamaki.com/content/images/size/w1200/2025/10/glitchEffect.jpg)

![Image](https://forums.cdprojektred.com/data/attachments/151/151598-cafdcc342964cbbb3ac87336e7a330dc.jpg)

Each mech has a **Timeline Track**.

Players draft:

* Rewind Core
* Pre-Fire Predictor
* Temporal Shield
* Future Echo Cannon

Example interactions:

* Rewind Shield → resets shield to 2 seconds ago
* Future Echo → fires ghost projectile from future state
* Time Split → duplicates mech state for 1.5 seconds

But:

Using too much temporal tech causes **Paradox Overload**.

If overload hits 100%:
→ Random module permanently disappears mid-fight.

High risk. High ceiling.

