# ⚖️ Scope Warning (Solo Dev Reality)

Don’t:

* Build full rigid-body simulation
* Build real-time PvP
* Add too many time mechanics early

Keep:

* Deterministic sim
* Limited timeline triggers
* Controlled physics approximation

Depth through interaction, not asset count.

